org.barghos.core.api.tuple

Interface ITup2fW

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ITupfW
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IVec2W
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Tup2f, Vec2f

    public interface ITup2fW
extends ITupfW
    This interface grants access to all writing methods of an 2-dimensional float tuple.
